content: Jianchao Li is a software engineer specialized in deep learning, machine learning and computer vision. He is honored to have been working as a software engineer and a site reliablity engineer at Indeed - the world’s #1 job site in Tokyo, Japan, as an algorithm engineer at ByteDance AI Lab in Beijing, China, and as a research engineer at ViSenze in Singapore.
